Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.63,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,用这个就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.63,0:09:28.21,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:31.50,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,是你专用的武器 支配之鞭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:34.47,ZH-Main-Down,,0,0,0,,这 这样之后要怎么做呢
